  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2013/11/25/spotify-connect-android/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/2b29a8637b4b027ef28c7e79169d5fca/2013-11-25_1211.png\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n几个月前，Spotify 团队为 iOS 版应用加入了 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/spotifyconnect\">Spotify Connect</a> 功能，让付费用户可以通过家庭 Wi-Fi 网络连接手机和喇叭，实现音乐播放无线控制。而到了今天，Android 版本终于也加入了同样的功能，用户只要拥有支持 Spotify Connect 的喇叭，便可获得同样的享受了。话虽如此，目前 Spotify 的官方合作伙伴只有先锋和 B&amp;O，而且适用 Spotify Connect 的也多为高端<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/24/spotify-connect/\">贵价产品</a>。这样看来，普及的路还很长啊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/25/spotify-connect-android/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.androidpolice.com/2013/11/25/spotify-connect-comes-to-android-latest-app-update-lets-premium-subscribers-stream-music-over-wi-fi-to-supported-speakers/\" target=\"_blank\">Android Police</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spotify.mobile.android.ui&amp;referrer=utm_source%3DPlayboard%26utm_medium%3DWidgetWeb%26utm_campaign%3DPlayboard\" target=\"_blank\">Google Play</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/25/android-spotify-spotify-connect/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20776206/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/25/android-spotify-spotify-connect/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
